表格报警配置的卡片

名称

报警配置

代码

CallConfig

数据库管理系统

Microsoft SQL Server 2005


表格报警配置的约束名称

CKT_CALLCONFIG


表格报警配置的服务器检验表达式

%RULES%


表格报警配置的选项

ON [PRIMARY]


表格报警配置的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('CallConfig')
and type = 'U')
drop table CallConfig
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: CallConfig */
/*==============================================================*/
create table CallConfig (
ID int identity(1,1),
CallID int not null,
CallStr varchar(100) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS not null,
CallTypeID int not null,
UnitType varchar(50) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS not null,
UnitTypeID int not null,
CallValue int not null,
UnitValue int not null,
CreateTime datetime not null constraint DF_CallConfig_CreateTime default CONVERT([char](19),getdate(),(121)),
MachineNo varchar(200) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS null,
DO_NO varchar(200) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS null,
SendNum int null,
upNum varchar(50) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS null,
downNum varchar(50) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS null,
sendEmployee varchar(200) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS null,
HuanMu varchar(400) null,
HuanLiao varchar(400) null,
HuanDan varchar(400) null,
FuShe varchar(400) null,
JiQi varchar(400) null,
MuJu varchar(400) null,
DaiLiao varchar(400) null,
WuDingDan varchar(400) null,
QiTa varchar(400) null,
DaiRen varchar(400) null,
ZiDingYi varchar(400) null,
constraint PK_CALLCONFIG primary key ()
WITH (IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
)
ON [PRIMARY]
go
